sub_title: MSc in Geo-Information Scince and Earth Observation for Natural Resources Management
summary:
•	Graduated with MSc degree in Geo-Information Science and Earth Observation for Natural Resources Management from, the Faculty of Geo-Information Science and Earth Observation (ITC), University of Twente, Enschede, The Netherlands in March 2015. 
•	Researcher on Environmental Management, Forestry and Image Analysis 
•	Bachelor of Art in Geography from the University of Asmara, Eritrea.
•	Worked as a teacher both at local and international schools.
•	Apply basic principles of geography, mapping, physical and computer based analysis of spatial phenomena, assist GIS specialists and engineering professionals on project plan preparations and design, evaluate, report of works.
